{
  "doc_id": "22417",
  "text": "The plasma LH concentration was assayed by a RIA double-antibody method, using antiovine-LH and antirabbit-gammaglobulin antisera and bovine LH standard (NIH-LH-B6) according to [CITATION_1] . The assay sensitivity was 0.3 ng/ml, and the intra-and interassay coefficients of variation were 8.2 and 12.5%, respectively.",
